    <h2>8. {{ current_year }} Economic Outlook</h2>
    <p class="sec-lead">
      The first months of 2026 have brought more change to Venezuela&rsquo;s
      economic trajectory than the preceding five years combined. Here are the
      key developments shaping the outlook.
    </p>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="tl-item positive">
        <span class="tl-dot"></span>
        <div class="tl-date">January 10, 2026</div>
        <div class="tl-title">Political Transition</div>
