        <div class="tl-date">January 28, 2026</div>
        <div class="tl-title">Hydrocarbon Law Reform</div>
        <div class="tl-desc">
          The interim government enacts sweeping changes to the 2001 Organic
          Hydrocarbons Law: reduced royalties, IOC operatorship, 40-year
          contracts, and international arbitration provisions.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tl-item positive">
        <span class="tl-dot"></span>
        <div class="tl-date">February 2026</div>
        <div class="tl-title">OFAC General Licenses 50A &amp; 52</div>
        <div class="tl-desc">
          OFAC issues GL 50A (authorizing oil and gas operations) and GL 52
          (authorizing new investment), reopening Venezuela to US-person
